				\begin{document}$$ \sigma_{k}^{2} = 0 $$\end{document}</tex-math><inline-graphic xlink:href="10709_2010_9497_Article_IEq10.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> can be used as initial for all <inline-formula id="IEq11"><alternatives><tex-math id="M16">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
